<header>

# Setup
1. Install JRE/JDK as suggested
2. Using brew/cask install intellij-ce
3. Update idea.properties and idea.vmoptions, Info.plist as needed
4. Start intellij
5. Install IdeaVim
6. Install Solarized Settings ( https://github.com/jkaving/intellij-colors-solarized )
&. Import Keyboard Shortcuts Settings ( TODO )

# Resources
* /Applications/IntelliJ IDEA 14 CE.app/Contents/bin/idea.properties
* /Applications/IntelliJ IDEA 14 CE.app/Contents/bin/idea.vmoptions
* /Applications/IntelliJ IDEA 14 CE.app/Contents/bin/Info.plist

* Preferences : 
  * ~/Library/Preferences/IdeaIC14

* Vim Keymap : 
  * /Users/sdoddame/Library/Preferences/IdeaIC14/keymaps/Vim.xml
  * ~/.ideavimrc

* Idea log : 
  * tail -F ~/Library/Logs/IdeaIC14/idea.log
